00:39:48,119 --> 00:39:49,954
Do you want some cake? It's on me.

805
00:39:50,488 --> 00:39:51,556
-Really?
-Yeah.

806
00:39:51,723 --> 00:39:53,091
Whatever you want.

807
00:39:55,126 --> 00:39:58,162
I'm so sorry for troubling you.

808
00:39:58,663 --> 00:40:01,099
I had a terrible boyfriend,

809
00:40:01,165 --> 00:40:03,301
so everyone was worried about me.

810
00:40:03,835 --> 00:40:06,237
I should say thank you to Daoming Si.

811
00:40:06,504 --> 00:40:08,940
If he didn't realize
how terrible Zhongze was,

812
00:40:09,007 --> 00:40:10,909
he wouldn't hit him.

813
00:40:10,975 --> 00:40:13,444
I made the tension
between Shancai and him so high.

814
00:40:14,879 --> 00:40:16,381
Have they made peace with each other?

815
00:40:16,447 --> 00:40:18,283
There's no peace between them.

816
00:40:18,349 --> 00:40:19,984
They're like this all year round.

817
00:40:20,885 --> 00:40:22,053
Could I have this one?

818
00:40:22,420 --> 00:40:23,388
Sure.

819
00:40:28,126 --> 00:40:30,094
Do you know about their trial period?

820
00:40:30,795 --> 00:40:31,663
Yeah.

821
00:40:31,729 --> 00:40:32,697
In two months,

822
00:40:32,764 --> 00:40:34,732
if they can't adapt to each other,

823
00:40:34,999 --> 00:40:36,534
they will break up?

824
00:40:36,701 --> 00:40:39,270
That's why I brought up
the idea of a double date.

825
00:40:39,470 --> 00:40:41,572
I didn't know I would make things worse.

826
00:40:42,040 --> 00:40:42,874
Yeah.

827
00:40:42,941 --> 00:40:44,776
We, bystanders, are worried like crazy.

828
00:40:45,143 --> 00:40:47,145
The two months will be over in no time.

829
00:40:47,645 --> 00:40:48,980
But those two idiots,

830
00:40:49,047 --> 00:40:51,182
they don't even know
what lovers should do.

831
00:40:58,056 --> 00:40:58,957
Xiaoyou.

832
00:40:59,457 --> 00:41:00,825
Could you do me a favor?

833
00:41:00,892 --> 00:41:02,060
Yeah.

834
00:41:02,126 --> 00:41:03,161
Go on a date with me.

835
00:41:04,963 --> 00:41:06,297
10 a.m. tomorrow.

836
00:41:12,136 --> 00:41:13,037
Where's Ximen?

837
00:41:13,104 --> 00:41:14,105
Did you see him?

838
00:41:14,372 --> 00:41:16,007
I don't know.
He said he got something to do.

839
00:41:16,074 --> 00:41:17,075
He won't be here.

840
00:41:17,141 --> 00:41:18,876
He seems to go on a date
with his new target.

841
00:41:19,143 --> 00:41:20,345
New target?

842
00:41:20,845 --> 00:41:22,180
He mustn't do that.

843
00:41:23,214 --> 00:41:26,084
Daoming Si, no matter what
you have to help me this time.

844
00:41:27,118 --> 00:41:29,287
We didn't know
you've made peace with each other.

845
00:41:29,354 --> 00:41:30,254
Lei.

846
00:41:30,321 --> 00:41:32,390
We must miss some critical plot points.

847
00:41:37,128 --> 00:41:39,063
What favor are you talking about?

848
00:41:40,631 --> 00:41:41,532
Right.

849
00:41:41,599 --> 00:41:43,534
Ximen. That playboy.

850
00:41:43,601 --> 00:41:45,403
He is going on a date with Xiaoyou.

851
00:41:45,470 --> 00:41:47,005
Xiaoyou just broke up.

852
00:41:47,071 --> 00:41:48,973
If she is hurt again by Ximen,

853
00:41:49,040 --> 00:41:50,074
she will be so sad.

854
00:41:50,141 --> 00:41:51,576
You have to help me with this.

855
00:41:53,011 --> 00:41:54,779
Why did Ximen suddenly change his taste?

856
00:41:56,114 --> 00:41:57,982
Shancai, you could think of it this way.

857
00:41:58,416 --> 00:42:00,284
Xiaoyou will grow up one day.

858
00:42:00,351 --> 00:42:03,054
Ximen could be the one popping her cherry.

859
00:42:03,121 --> 00:42:04,155
He mustn't do that.

860
00:42:04,222 --> 00:42:05,056
Daoming Si, please.

861
00:42:05,123 --> 00:42:06,724
You have to stop Ximen.

862
00:42:06,791 --> 00:42:08,926
Shancai, don't listen
to Meizuo's nonsense.

863
00:42:08,993 --> 00:42:10,528
Ximen has a good moral compass.

864
00:42:10,595 --> 00:42:11,462
No.

865
00:42:11,529 --> 00:42:14,465
I can't sit here and watch Xiaoyou
staying around the big bad wolf Ximen.

866
00:42:14,532 --> 00:42:15,633
I care about her well-being.

867
00:42:15,700 --> 00:42:18,469
Daoming Si, please.
You have to stop Ximen.

868
00:42:19,670 --> 00:42:20,605
Well...

869
00:42:20,671 --> 00:42:21,806
This is nonsense.

870
00:42:21,973 --> 00:42:23,374
Shancai, we are F4,

871
00:42:23,441 --> 00:42:25,076
but each of us has his personal freedom.

872
00:42:25,143 --> 00:42:27,245
Ah Si, you won't stop them, will you?

873
00:42:27,512 --> 00:42:28,579
I...

874
00:42:29,847 --> 00:42:31,215
I can't do this.

875
00:42:32,884 --> 00:42:35,053
How about this?
I send someone to follow them.

876
00:42:35,119 --> 00:42:36,421
So Xiaoyou won't be in any danger.

877
00:42:36,487 --> 00:42:37,422
This will do, right?

878
00:42:37,488 --> 00:42:38,856
Xiaoyou can't be in danger.

879
00:42:38,923 --> 00:42:40,058
What are you implying?

880
00:42:40,124 --> 00:42:42,493
Do you mean
Ximen is a venomous snake or a beast?

881
00:42:42,660 --> 00:42:45,096
I'll just send someone to follow them.
I won't meddle with their date.

882
00:42:45,997 --> 00:42:47,131
Lei, what do you think?

883
00:43:19,297 --> 00:43:20,932
Did you have any trouble
finding this place?

884
00:43:22,767 --> 00:43:25,169
This is owned
by an Italian friend of mine.

885
00:43:25,536 --> 00:43:27,638
It's a pretty interesting family cafe.

886
00:43:27,972 --> 00:43:29,774
Their coffee is legit.

887
00:43:30,108 --> 00:43:31,175
Do you want a cup of coffee?

888
00:43:31,776 --> 00:43:32,810
Okay.

889
00:43:32,877 --> 00:43:33,978
What would you like to drink?

890
00:43:34,479 --> 00:43:37,115
Anything is fine.
I know nothing about this anyway.

891
00:43:37,181 --> 00:43:38,683
-Then let me order for you.
-Okay.

892
00:43:39,750 --> 00:43:40,918
Excuse me.

893
00:43:41,085 --> 00:43:42,186
Espresso.

894
00:43:44,856 --> 00:43:47,058
If we go on a date like this,

895
00:43:47,125 --> 00:43:49,127
Shancai and Daoming Si won't see us.

896
00:43:49,193 --> 00:43:50,394
Will it work?

897
00:43:50,461 --> 00:43:52,230
I've told them our date.

898
00:43:52,730 --> 00:43:54,532
Shancai is always making a fuss
about everything.

899
00:43:54,599 --> 00:43:56,534
She'll do everything she can
to find out our location.

900
00:43:57,568 --> 00:44:00,404
To make her more paranoid,

901
00:44:01,072 --> 00:44:02,507
you should call her right now.

902
00:44:05,209 --> 00:44:08,346
But I don't know
if I will act well enough.

903
00:44:08,813 --> 00:44:10,515
I'm afraid I'll blow our cover.

904
00:44:10,581 --> 00:44:12,250
Just tell her what I taught you.

905
00:44:12,483 --> 00:44:13,784
With Shancai's personality,

906
00:44:13,851 --> 00:44:17,221
she won't be able to think straight
when she's nervous.

907
00:45:52,416 --> 00:45:54,452
Subtitle translation by Logan Zhao
